OL,3,CMartyn's Law receives Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FA proposed law that aims to prevent
OL,7,Fand reduce the harm of terror attacks
OL,8,Fat event venues has received Royal
OL,9,FAssent, after more than six years of
OL,10,Fcampaigning.
OL,12,FMartyn's Law was first suggested by
OL,13,FFigen Murray OBE after she lost her 29-
OL,14,Fyear-old son Martyn Hett in the
OL,15,FManchester Arena bombing in May 2017.
