OL,3,CMartyn's Law receives Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FFigen Murray has welcomed the
OL,7,Fsignificant moment, saying the "much
OL,8,Fneeded" law will secure her son's
OL,9,Flegacy and prevent other families from
OL,10,Fgoing through what she and 21 others
OL,11,Fhad to endure.
OL,13,FFigen, the initiator of Martyn's Law,
OL,14,Fsaid: "My son Martyn Hett was murdered
OL,15,Falongside 21 innocent victims in the
OL,16,FManchester Arena terror attack on 22
OL,17,FMay 2017, and whilst nothing will
OL,18,Fbring Martyn back, I am determined to
OL,19,Fensure nobody endures what my family
OL,20,Fhas experienced.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
