OL,3,CMartyn's Law receives Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,F"For the last six years I have
OL,7,Fcampaigned to introduce measures that
OL,8,Fwill improve security at public venues
OL,9,Fand how they respond to a terror
OL,10,Fattack - Martyn's Law.
OL,12,F"I am grateful to the Prime Minister,
OL,13,Fthe Security Minister and Lord Hanson
OL,14,Ffor how quickly they've progressed
OL,15,FMartyn's Law through parliament. But
OL,16,Fthis would not have happened without
OL,17,Fthe tireless support of my co-
OL,18,Fcampaigners Nick Aldworth, Brendan
OL,19,FCox, Nathan Emmerich, my husband
OL,20,FStuart, and my children.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
