OL,3,CMartyn's Law receives Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,F"Over the implementation period it is
OL,7,Fvital that the government and Security
OL,8,FIndustry Authority provide all that is
OL,9,Fnecessary for publicly accessible
OL,10,Flocations to implement Martyn's Law."
OL,12,FSpeaking on Thursday, Prime Minister
OL,13,FSir Keir Starmer said: "Today is a
OL,14,Flandmark moment for our security as my
OL,15,Fgovernment delivers on its promise to
OL,16,Fintroduce Martyn's Law and better
OL,17,Fprotect the public from terrorism.
OL,26,@uD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
