OL,3,CMartyn's Law receives Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,F"Figen's courage and determination in
OL,7,Fthe face of such unimaginable loss is
OL,8,Ftruly humbling and it is thanks to her
OL,9,Fcampaigning that Martyn's Law means
OL,10,Fher son's legacy will live on forever.
OL,12,F"Security is the foundation of our
OL,13,FPlan for Change and the first duty of
OL,14,Fany government. Martyn's Law will
OL,15,Fensure everyone can enjoy public
OL,16,Fevents more safely and ensure venues
OL,17,Facross the country have clear,
OL,18,Fpractical measures in place to protect
OL,19,Fpeople."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU{D@HO]
