OL,6,FHome Secretary, Yvette Cooper added:
OL,7,F"Martyn's Law will significantly
OL,8,Fstrengthen public safety across our
OL,9,Fcountry, I'd like to thank Figen
OL,10,FMurray for her tireless work to make
OL,11,Fthis law a reality
OL,13,FWhat is Martyn's Law?
OL,15,FFigen began campaigning for tougher
OL,16,Fsecurity measures after she went to a
OL,17,Fconcert in Salford 18 months after the
OL,18,FManchester Arena attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
