OL,3,CMartyn's Law receives Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FTo her horror, she realised that no
OL,7,Fsecurity seemed to be in place - the
OL,8,Fsmall bag she was carrying was not
OL,9,Feven checked.
OL,11,FShortly afterwards, Figen decided to
OL,12,Flaunch a government petition calling
OL,13,Ffor "Martyn's Law".
OL,15,FWhat would Martyn's Law mean?
OL,17,FThe introduction of Martyn's Law,
OL,18,Fofficially titled the Terrorism
OL,19,F(Protection of Premises) Bill, will
OL,20,Fmake it a legal requirement for public
OL,21,Fplaces to improve security measures.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
