OL,3,CMartyn's Law receives Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FThose responsible for premises will be
OL,7,Frequired to fulfil necessary but
OL,8,Fproportionate steps, according to
OL,9,Ftheir capacity, to help keep the
OL,10,Fpublic safe.
OL,12,FThis includes a tiered approach,
OL,13,Flinked to the size of the venue, how
OL,14,Fmany people will be there and the
OL,15,Factivity taking place, making sure
OL,16,Fundue burdens are not placed on small
OL,17,Fbusinesses.
OL,19,FA standard tier premises will apply to
OL,20,Flocations with a capacity of more than
OL,21,F200 people but under 800.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
