OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FWill Martyn's law apply to the whole
OL,7,Fof the UK?
OL,9,FThe legislation will apply across
OL,10,FEngland, Wales, Scotland and Northern
OL,11,FIreland, as national security is a
OL,12,Freserved matter for the UK Government.
OL,14,FWhile the law will take at least two
OL,15,Fyears to come into force, in
OL,16,FManchester, training is already
OL,17,Funderway.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
