OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FCityCo (a company offering training to
OL,7,Fbusinesses ahead of the implementation
OL,8,Fof Martyn's Law): says 2,755 people
OL,9,Fhave attended the training and
OL,10,Freceived certificates, covering more
OL,11,Fthan 830 businesses in Manchester City
OL,12,FCentre.
OL,14,FOne business to take up the training
OL,15,Fwas legendary music venue Band on the
OL,16,FWall, situated less than a mile from
OL,17,Fthe Arena.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
