OL,3,CMartyn's Law receives Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FChief Operating Officer John Shepherd
OL,7,Ftold ITV News that shutters were one
OL,8,Fof a number of measures that have been
OL,9,Fbrought in as part of security
OL,10,Fprocedure in the event of a terrorist
OL,11,Fattack.
OL,13,FHe said: "We've undertaken
OL,14,Fvulnerability assessments, we have
OL,15,Fevacuation plans related to terrorist
OL,16,Fincidents, we have undertaken staff
OL,17,Ftraining provided by Manchester City
OL,18,FCouncil and CityCo.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/16
