OL,3,CMartyn's Law receives Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,F"The vulnerability assessments we've
OL,7,Fundertaken are to examine all aspects
OL,8,Fof the building and to see where are
OL,9,Fvulnerabilities to any kind of
OL,10,Fterrorist activities are.
OL,12,F"All of our staff have undertaken the
OL,13,FAction Counters Terrorism training."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
