OL,3,CMartyn's Law receives Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FNick Aldworth, former National
OL,7,FCoordinator for Protect and Prepare at
OL,8,FCounter Terrorism Policing, said: "I'm
OL,9,Fdelighted that this legislation now
OL,10,Fexists, it has been the missing piece
OL,11,Fof the jigsaw that was needed to
OL,12,Fcomplete the UK Counter-Terrorism
OL,13,Fstrategy.
OL,15,F"I pay tribute to my co-campaigner,
OL,16,FFigen Murray whose resilience and
OL,17,Fdetermination, while dealing with her
OL,18,Fown grief and the needs of her family,
OL,19,Fhas made this all possible.
OL,26,@pD@cOU
