OL,3,CMartyn's Law receives Royal Assent
OL,4,Cafter campaign by Martyn Hett's mother
OL,6,FBrendan Cox, co-founder of Survivors
OL,7,FAgainst Terror, said: "You should
OL,8,Fnever doubt what the courage, bravery
OL,9,Fand passion of a mother can achieve.
OL,11,F"This was never a quest for sympathy,
OL,12,Fit was a desire for change to make us
OL,13,Fall safer. Today Figen has achieved
OL,14,Fthat, and we all owe her a debt of
OL,15,Fthanks.
OL,17,F"After years of delay the Government
OL,18,Fhas got this on the statute book
OL,19,Fwithin months of coming into office
OL,20,Fand they deserve credit for that.
OL,26,@oD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
